No. 123,

Misc.

Reese v. Louisiana. Sam J. D’Amico for petitioner. Jack P. F. Gremillion, Attorney General of Louisiana, and Ralph L. Roy for respondent.

Sup. Ct. La. Certiorari denied.

Mr. Justice Douglas, Mr. Justice Fortas and Mr. Justice Marshall are of the opinion that certiorari should be granted.
